    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/21d1286e601a882c1cf2a273d867d3e5.avif?t=1749995266\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><strong>Slap Squad</strong> offers physics based animations and hectic 8 player online lobbies acting as a recipe for hilarious toon style random moments. You can slap, shoot or blow up your friends in multiple game modes each with a variety of world themes.<br>( Kindly note that Slap Squad <i>DOES NOT</i> currently offer a single player mode )<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/76bb6e87a61a52f6dd4367166d14ebab.poster.avif?t=1749995266\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/76bb6e87a61a52f6dd4367166d14ebab.webm?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/76bb6e87a61a52f6dd4367166d14ebab.mp4?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Whatever it takes...</h2>Fight over weapons, powerups and objectives like piranhas in a tank.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/5e1cdc338ecb0f449adac8dcde06be91.poster.avif?t=1749995266\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/5e1cdc338ecb0f449adac8dcde06be91.webm?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/5e1cdc338ecb0f449adac8dcde06be91.mp4?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slap Squad features game modes including:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Last Man Standing<br></li><li>Slap Tag<br></li><li>Ticking Bomb</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/707b5c9124ec807131342efd78c4e356.poster.avif?t=1749995266\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/707b5c9124ec807131342efd78c4e356.webm?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/707b5c9124ec807131342efd78c4e356.mp4?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Or you can dance it out with your buddies..</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/70a58c029b368eddfa75f9e2696a1ac6.poster.avif?t=1749995266\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/70a58c029b368eddfa75f9e2696a1ac6.webm?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128230/extras/70a58c029b368eddfa75f9e2696a1ac6.mp4?t=1749995266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you!</h2>Hello! Slap Squad is a game made by me (Omar). A solo Egyptian developer with a passion for games that have a humorous nature. If you decide to wishlist or purchase a copy of my game, I thank you and hope you'll enjoy playing it as much as I enjoyed creating it :D <br>Thanks again and have fun!",
